                    "line_text": "Crispe ses doigts crochus armés d'ongles de fer",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 4,
                    "line_text": "Pour me saisir : des feux pareils aux feux d'enfer",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Se croisent devant moi ; dans l'ombre des yeux fauves",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Rayonnent ; des vautours à cous rouges et chauves,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Battent mon front de l'aile en poussant des cris sourds :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "En vain pour me sauver je lève mes pieds lourds,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Des flots de plomb fondu subitement les baignent,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "A des pointes d'acier ils se heurtent et saignent,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Meurtris et disloqués ; et mon dos cependant",
