                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "Comme une scie aiguë, et des pinces qui tordent ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Ensuite le sol manque à mes pas chancelants :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Un gouffre me reçoit ; sur des rochers brûlants,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "Sur des pics anguleux que la lune reflète,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 22,
                    "line_text": "Tremblant je roule, roule, et j'arrive squelette",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "Dans un marais de sang ; bientôt, spectres hideux,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 24,
                    "line_text": "Des morts au teint bleuâtre en sortent deux à deux,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 25,
                    "line_text": "Et se penchant vers moi m'apprennent les mystères",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 26,
                    "line_text": "Que le trépas révèle aux pâles feudataires",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
